        {
            "title": "財經｜特步(01368)去年盈利升11% 息9.5仙",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜特步(01368)去年盈利升11% 息9.5仙\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜特步(01368)去年盈利升11% 息9.5仙</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特步國際(01368)公布，截至去年底止全年業績，股東應佔溢利13.72億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年增長10.76%。每股基本盈利51.35分，末期息派9.5港仙。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">期內，收入141.51億元，按年上升4.23%，主要受益於大眾運動分部收入上升1.5%至125億元；專業運動分部收入大幅增加30.8%，至16.36億元。毛利率42.8%，下跌0.4個百分點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至去年底止，集團於中國內地及海外分別共有6357間特步成人店舖及1488間特步少年店舖。索康尼在中國內地共有175間店舖。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特步國際稱，得益於積極的政府政策以及公眾健康意識的持續提升，體育用品行業的基本面維持穩健。行業的整體韌性，疊加公司獨特的運營靈活性，使特步對未來的發展前景充滿信心。公司已作好充分準備，戰略性地將短期波動轉化為增長機遇，為持份者持續創造價值。</p></div>",
