        {
            "title": "DEEP WATER SOUTH 6A期原價加推93伙｜折實均呎2.8萬  低首批約3.3%｜本周六次輪發售99伙",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">會德豐地產與港鐵合作發展的黃竹坑站港島南岸第6期DEEP WATER SOUTH，其第6A期MONT BLUE公布第2號價單。新價單提供93伙，戶型涵蓋一至兩房，折實均呎為28,105元。相比本月13日公布的首張價單折實均呎29,055元，新一批單位的折實均呎低約3.27%，整體定價水平相若，屬原價加推。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">項目將於本周六（28日）進行次輪銷售，其中93伙以價單形式發售，另有6伙以招標形式推出。銷售安排劃分為三個買家組別。S組及A組主要供有意購入多伙單位的買家參與，B組則供購入1至2伙單位的買家參與。其中，S組專為曾購入第6B期單位的買家而設，可認購1至4伙指定單位；A組買家則可認購3至8伙指定單位。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6c4c71a3-c7e5-308c-9c35-f5fcb372ae56-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"DEEP WATER SOUTH 6A期價單\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:DEEP WATER SOUTH 6A期價單;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4lNa5Pm\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">DEEP WATER SOUTH 6A期價單</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"DEEP WATER SOUTH｜黃竹坑站上蓋最後一期 發展商先招標、後開價 有何考量\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:DEEP WATER SOUTH｜黃竹坑站上蓋最後一期 發展商先招標、後開價 有何考量;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4stMqWN\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">DEEP WATER SOUTH｜黃竹坑站上蓋最後一期 發展商先招標、後開價 有何考量</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>原價加推第2號價單 折實均呎約2.8萬</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">DEEP WATER SOUTH第6A期於本周二（24日）公布第2號價單，加推93伙，戶型包括39伙一房（開放式廚房）、39伙兩房（開放式廚房）及15伙兩房一套（梗廚）單位，實用面積介乎337至563平方呎。以定價計算，該批單位市值約12.4億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">扣除最高15%折扣後，新一批單位折實售價介乎886.5萬至1,829.7萬元，折實呎價介乎26,306至32,499元，折實均呎為28,105元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相比本月13日公布的首張價單折實均呎29,055元，新一批單位折實均呎低約3.27%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>一房入場折實887萬起 兩房1,067萬起</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">綜觀第2號價單各戶型，一房（開放式廚房）的入場單位為第2座(2A)9樓F室，實用面積337平方呎，折實售價約886.5萬元。此單位亦是該批價單中折實呎價最低的單位，折實呎價約26,306元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VIxOw_YP2RHdNSxvweW_7Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/917034ba8ba83d085644ac079e307377\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兩房單位之中，入場單位屬開放式廚房戶型，單位為第2座(2C)9樓E室，實用面積399平方呎，折實售價約1,067.2萬元，折實呎價約26,746元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eKC77T0ANzgvyOoUisG7XQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/876a4559c7c8d38cfafd35e48879cc3d\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外，該批折實呎價最高的單位，為第2座(2C)40樓C室的兩房（梗廚）單位，實用面積563平方呎，折實售價約1,829.7萬元，折實呎價約32,499元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>項目背景與地價</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由會德豐地產與港鐵合作發展的DEEP WATER SOUTH第6A期MONT BLUE，位於香港仔及鴨脷洲香葉道11號。該項目屬黃竹坑港鐵站上蓋最後一期住宅發展，位處整個發展項目的東北面，鄰近港鐵站。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">項目建有一幢住宅大樓，內部細分為2A、2B及2C座，合共提供463伙。單位設有一至三房間隔，實用面積介乎297至2,011平方呎。校網方面，小學隸屬18校網，中學屬於南區。項目的預計關鍵日期為2027年5月30日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">翻查地價數據，該期數的最高可建住宅樓面面積約50.4萬平方呎，補地價金額約49.4億元，折合每平方呎約9,818元。若連同建築成本等計算，預計每平方呎樓面地價約1.6萬至1.8萬元，估計項目市值約81億至91億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Deep Water South 6A期\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:Deep Water South 6A期;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/deep-water-south-6A期\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Deep Water South 6A期</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"港島南岸\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:港島南岸;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/港島南岸-27919\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">港島南岸</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"香港仔\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:香港仔;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/香港仔-27333\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">香港仔</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"黃竹坑\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:黃竹坑;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/黃竹坑-27361\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">黃竹坑</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"鴨脷洲\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:鴨脷洲;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/鴨脷洲-27362\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">鴨脷洲</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"南區\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:南區;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/南區-27335\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">南區</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"新聞連結\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/DEEP-WATER-SOUTH-6A%E6%9C%9F%E5%8E%9F%E5%83%B9%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A893%E4%BC%99-%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6%E5%9D%87%E5%91%8E2-8%E8%90%AC-%E4%BD%8E%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E7%B4%843-3-%E6%9C%AC%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E6%AC%A1%E8%BC%AA%E7%99%BC%E5%94%AE99%E4%BC%99-75274\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"28Hse App\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse App;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/appdownload\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse App</a>。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/deep-water-south-6a%E6%9C%9F%E5%8E%9F%E5%83%B9%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A893%E4%BC%99-%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6%E5%9D%87%E5%91%8E2-045207061.html",
